  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育网络环境下的ARP协议序列图，展示四台学生电脑通过交换机通信的过程。场景是Computadora A要找Computadora C，但一开始不知道它的MAC地址。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora C",
        "Switch",
        "ARP Request",
        "ARP Response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这是一个典型的ARP解析流程。我注意到您提到了四台电脑，除了A和C，另外两台是B和D吗？它们在这个场景里扮演什么角色？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，四台分别是Computadora A、B、C、D。B和D会收到广播，但只有C会响应。另外我想给每台电脑标注对应的教育系统模块，比如A关联Education_ContentCDN，C关联Education_GradeSync。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Computadora C",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我打算从左到右排列参与者：A、Switch、B、C、D。Switch我标注为Education_StudentDB，因为它充当学生数据库的中枢。开头先加一个注释说明交换机的MAC表是空的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Tabla MAC vacía"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，但B、C、D的位置让我再想想——其实Switch应该在中间，四台电脑都连到它上面。所以参与者顺序应该是A、S、B、C、D，其中S代表Switch。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora C",
        "Computadora D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "调整了布局。现在第一阶段是ARP请求，A发送广播找目标。这里A的源标识应该是Education_StudentDB，广播目标是Education_LMS_Portal，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARP Request",
        "Computadora A",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Broadcast",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "稍等，这里有个细节要确认。A发起ARP请求时，它的源模块标识确实是Education_StudentDB，但广播目标是Education_LMS_Portal——这代表LMS门户的广播域。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARP Request",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Origen",
        "Destino"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了。我在Switch上加个注释：学习到端口1对应A的MAC地址。然后Switch把ARP请求转发给B、C、D三台电脑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Puerto 1",
        "MAC de A",
        "ARP Request",
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora C",
        "Computadora D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "转发的时候标注一下每个请求对应的教育模块：给B的是Education_ClassroomService，给C的是Education_GradeSync，给D的是Education_ContentCDN。这样能看出不同系统的分布。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARP Request",
        "Computadora B",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Computadora C",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Computadora D",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已添加。接下来需要说明B和D收到广播但不会响应，只有C会回复。我打算在B和D上方加一个跨两者的注释。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora D",
        "Solo C responde al ARP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，然后进入第二阶段ARP响应。C直接向A回复，这时候目标已经明确是A了，所以是单播。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FASE 2",
        "ARP Response",
        "Computadora C",
        "Computadora A"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "C回复时，源模块标识应该是Education_ContentCDN，目标A对应Education_GradeSync，这样和之前的模块分配保持一致。确认一下这个对应关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARP Response",
        "Computadora C",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Computadora A",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Origen",
        "Destino"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认。这里有个容易混淆的点：A最初是Education_ContentCDN，但作为ARP响应的目标时，它对应Education_GradeSync。模块标识是根据通信上下文变化的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "ARP Response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在Switch上加注释：学习到端口3对应C的MAC地址。然后Switch把ARP响应转发给A，标注为Education_LMS_Portal。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Puerto 3",
        "MAC de C",
        "ARP Response",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "现在进入第三阶段：直接通信。A已经知道C的MAC地址，可以发送数据了。数据包的源模块是Education_ClassroomService，目标是Education_ContentCDN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FASE 3",
        "Comunicación Directa",
        "Datos",
        "Computadora A",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Computadora C",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里我需要确认：第三阶段A发送数据时，源模块变成了Education_ClassroomService，而第一阶段ARP请求时源是Education_StudentDB。这是业务逻辑的变化还是标注方式不同？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Datos",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "ARP Request",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Computadora A"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好问题。第一阶段ARP是网络层行为，用Education_StudentDB表示学生数据库查询；第三阶段是应用层数据传输，用Education_ClassroomService表示课堂服务。同一台电脑在不同阶段扮演不同角色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARP Request",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Datos",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Capa de red",
        "Capa de aplicación"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了。我在Switch上加注释：查询MAC表，发现C在端口3。然后Switch直接把数据转发给C，不再广播。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Consulta tabla MAC",
        "Puerto 3",
        "Datos",
        "Computadora C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后一步，数据到达C时标注为Education_ClassroomService，保持端到端的模块一致性。另外我想确认一下D的标注——D也是Education_ContentCDN，和A一样，这会造成混淆吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Datos",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Computadora D",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Computadora A"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确实，A和D都是Education_ContentCDN，但A是发起方，D只是收到广播的旁观者。这在实际系统中常见吗？比如内容分发节点既有客户端也有服务端角色？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora D",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Cliente",
        "Servidor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，ContentCDN节点可以是请求方也可以是提供方。在这个场景里A请求内容，D是另一个内容节点但没参与这次通信。这样设计能体现CDN的对等特性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora D",
        "CDN",
        "Peer-to-peer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了三个阶段的绘制。我再检查一下：第一阶段ARP广播，Switch学习A的MAC；第二阶段C单播响应，Switch学习C的MAC；第三阶段单播数据直达。所有模块标注都已对应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FASE 1",
        "FASE 2",
        "FASE 3",
        "ARP Request",
        "ARP Response",
        "Datos",
        "Switch",
        "Tabla MAC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我注意到第一阶段A的ARP请求目标标注是Broadcast (Education_LMS_Portal)，但第三阶段A发送数据的目标标注是C (Education_ContentCDN)。这里Education_ContentCDN和Education_LMS_Portal的关系需要明确吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Broadcast",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Computadora C",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Destino"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "您说得对，我检查一下——实际上第三阶段的目标C标注为Education_ContentCDN是正确的，因为C作为ContentCDN节点响应了请求。但让我再确认：第一阶段广播目标是Education_LMS_Portal，这是LMS系统的广播域标识，不是具体节点。这个区分在图里需要更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FASE 1",
